====== H238: אָזַן (ʼâzan) ======

===== Source =====

a primitive root; probably to  ; but used only as a denominative from  H241 ;

===== Meaning =====

expand to  broaden out the ear  (with the hand), i.e. (by implication) to  listen

===== Definitions =====

  - expand
  - broaden out the ear
  - listen

===== Usage =====

give (perceive by the) ear, hear(-ken). See 
